      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tas notiḱs tai Deenâ/ tad dohſchu es Gogam weenu Rappeni eekſch Israëka/ to Eelei- ju kur prett Rihta Puſti pahr- eect pee Juhras/ ta kas fezzen to ees/ to Deggonu aisturrehs/ un tur apraks tee Gogu/ un wiﬀu winna Pulku/ un nofauks to/ to Eeleiju no Goga Pulka.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tas Israëta Nams ap- raks tohs/ tadeht ka ta Semme tohp tchkihſtita ſeptinôs Mehne- khôs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ir wiſſi Laudis tahs Semmes to apraks un tas buhs teem par weenu Slawu / tai Deenâ kad es buhſchu pagohdi- najees/ fakka tas Kungs KUNgs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ir tee tur nospreedihg Wihrus/ kas bes Mitteſchanas zaur to Semmi pahreet/ un tohs Rappu-Razzejus ar teem / kas zaur staiga/ un aprohk tohs at- lizzinatus Semmes Wirſi/ to paschu fchkibſtiht / ap ſeptinau Mehneſchu Gallu tee iſwaiſahs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tchee Pahrſtaigataji ees zaur to Semmi/ un kas Zil- weka Kanlu redſ/ tas darrihs weenu Sihmi pee ta/ kamebr tee Kappu-Razzejt to irr aprakku- ſchi/ tai Eeleija no Goga Pulka.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ir ta Pillsfahta Wahrs buhs Amona/ ta tchkibſtihs tee to Semmi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tu tad ak Zilweka Behrns! Ta fakka tas Kungs KUNGS: Sakki us wiﬀeem\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "spahrnatceem Putneem/ un us wiﬀeem Swchreem wirs Sem- mes: Sapulzejeetes/ un nahzet klaht/fakrahjeetees no tahm wiﬀ- apkahrtjahn Weetahn pee man- na Uppura/ ko es preekſch juns ejmu uppurejs/ weenu leelu Up- puri us Israëta Kalneem/ un eh- dect Gattu/un dserreet Afﬁni.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jums buhs to Gattu to Warreno ehſt/ un to Afﬁni to Leel-Kunng wirs Semmes dsert/ to Awenu/ to Annu un Abschu/ un Wehrſchu/ kas wiſſi barroti un taukt irr.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un jums buhs tohs Tau- kus ehſt/ kamehr juhs pee-ehdat/ un to Afﬁni dsert/ kamehr juhs peedsexratees/ no manna Uppu- ra / ko es preekſch jums ejmu kawis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un juhs tapfeet pee-ehdi- nati pee manna Galda/ no Sir- geem un Jahtneekeem/ no stip- reem un wiﬀadeim Kaxa-Wih- reein/ fakka tas Kungs KUNgs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Es eezelfchu mannu Sohdibu to Pagaxu Starpâ/ un wiſſi Pagaxi redsehe man- nu Sohdibu/ ko es ejmu darrijs/ un mannu Rohku/ ko es pee teem ejmu peelizzigs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tee no Israëta Nam- ma fajuttihe/ ka es tas KUNgs winnu Deevs ejmu / no tahs Deenas un ta probjam.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tee Pagaxi fajuttihs/ ka tee no Israëta Namma favvu Noseegunn deht irr aistvesti/ ta- pehz ka tee prett manni bij pahr- rahpu-\n"
    }
  ],
